        <div class="text center xxl-spacing-top text-block con-block" data-block-status="loaded" data-block="">
          <div class="foreground">
            <div class="body-m">
              <h2 id="the-adobe-difference" class="heading-xl">The Adobe difference.</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section three-up xxl-spacing" data-has-placeholders="true">
        <div class="icon-block vertical small s-spacing-bottom con-block" data-block-status="loaded" data-block="">
          <div class="foreground">
            <div class="text-content">
              <p class="icon-area"><picture><img loading="lazy" src="/cc-shared/assets/img/business/teams/plans/s2-icon-globegrid-20-n.svg" alt=""></picture></p>
              <h3 id="were-a-trusted-global-brand" class="heading-s">We’re a trusted global brand.</h3>
              <p class="body-m">Companies around the world rely on Adobe’s&nbsp;innovations — from creativity and productivity apps like Adobe Photoshop and Acrobat to cutting-edge technologies like Adobe Firefly generative AI — to imagine, create, and bring any digital experience to life.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-block vertical small s-spacing-bottom con-block" data-block-status="loaded" data-block="">
          <div class="foreground">
            <div class="text-content">
              <p class="icon-area"><picture><img loading="lazy" src="/cc-shared/assets/img/business/teams/plans/s2-icon-lightbulb-20-n.svg" alt=""></picture></p>
              <h3 id="we-have-solutions-for-every-business" class="heading-s">We have solutions for every business.</h3>
              <p class="body-m">From small businesses to the world’s largest enterprises, our customers use our integrated Creative Cloud, Document Cloud, and Experience Cloud solutions to unleash their creativity, accelerate document productivity, optimize the customer experience, and power their digital businesses.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-block vertical small s-spacing-bottom con-block" data-block-status="loaded" data-block="">
          <div class="foreground">
            <div class="text-content">
              <p class="icon-area"><picture><img loading="lazy" src="/cc-shared/assets/img/business/teams/plans/s2-icon-callcenter-20-n.svg" alt=""></picture></p>
              <h3 id="we-have-your-back" class="heading-s">We have your back.</h3>
              <p class="body-m">We provide our business customers with 24x7x365 support for all their licensing and troubleshooting needs. Our Creative Cloud Pro plans also include 1:1 sessions with Adobe product experts.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section-metadata" data-block-status="loaded">
          <div>
            <div>style</div>
            <div>three-up, xxl spacing</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section static-links xxl-spacing" data-has-placeholders="true"><div class="content" data-block=""><h2 id="frequently-asked-questions">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
        
        <div class="accordion-container max-width-12-desktop-large xxl-spacing-bottom con-block" data-block-status="loaded" data-block=""><div class="descr-list accordion foreground" id="accordion-1" role="presentation"><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-1" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-1" daa-ll="open-1--What does Creative Cloud for teams include">
            What does Creative Cloud for teams include?
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-1" id="accordion-1-content-1" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>
              <p>Creative Cloud for teams provides businesses of all sizes access to 20+ creative apps including Photoshop, Illustrator, and Acrobat Pro, as well as tools for simplified administration and IP protection.</p>
              <p>All plans include 1TB of cloud storage per user, enabling team members to easily share files, view company assets, and collaborate effectively through features like shared libraries, link sharing, and co-editing.</p>
            </div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-2" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-2" daa-ll="open-2--How is Creative Cloud for teams different from Creative Cloud for individuals and enterprise">
            How is Creative Cloud for teams different from Creative Cloud for individuals and enterprise?
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-2" id="accordion-1-content-2" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>
              <p>Creative Cloud for teams is designed for businesses with enhanced collaboration and control. It includes everything in our Creative Cloud for individuals plans but does not include the advanced security, license management, and support of enterprise plans.</p>
              <p>Creative Cloud for teams plans include:</p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Pooled storage:</strong> 1TB per user, shared across the team</li>
                <li><strong>Shared resources:</strong> Company-owned libraries accessible to all</li>
                <li><strong>Extended history:</strong> 180-day version histories for cloud documents</li>
                <li><strong>Asset protection:</strong> Ability to reclaim assets from departing team members</li>
                <li><strong>Simplified management:</strong> Web-based admin console and centralized IT tools</li>
                <li><strong>Dedicated support:</strong> 24/7 technical support and expert 1:1 sessions</li>
                <li><strong>Complimentary membership:</strong> All company employees get access to Adobe Express, Acrobat Online Services, and ability to view company files, custom fonts, and more</li>
                <li><strong>Talent acquisition:</strong> Unlimited job posts on Behance</li>
              </ul>
              <p>The enterprise plan adds exclusive generative AI features, centralized deployment and access controls, single sign-on (SSO), and unlimited support from Adobe product experts.</p>
            </div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-3" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-3" daa-ll="open-3--How many users can use a single license">
            How many users can use a single license?
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-3" id="accordion-1-content-3" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Each license is assigned to a single user on a team. That user can sign in to Creative Cloud apps on up to two computers at a time.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-4" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-4" daa-ll="open-4--Are there Creative Cloud training resources available for our team">
            Are there Creative Cloud training resources available for our team?
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-4" id="accordion-1-content-4" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, Adobe is invested in helping your team successfully create high-quality content. You can access many hands-on tutorials, videos, and articles on <a href="/learn/">Adobe Learn</a>.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-5" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-5" daa-ll="open-5--Members of my organization already have individual Creative Cloud memberships Can I switch them to Creative Cloud for teams">
            Members of my organization already have individual Creative Cloud memberships. Can I switch them to Creative Cloud for teams?
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-5" id="accordion-1-content-5" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Yes, team members with individual Creative Cloud memberships can upgrade to Creative Cloud for teams with no cancellation fee. To do so, call <a href="tel:%7b%7bphone-number-cct%7d%7d">800-915-9428</a> or use <a href="/creativecloud/business/">chat</a> for support.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-6" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-6" daa-ll="open-6--Can I use Creative Cloud for teams on multiple computers">
            Can I use Creative Cloud for teams on multiple computers?
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-6" id="accordion-1-content-6" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>Your Creative Cloud for teams subscription lets you activate each of the 20+ Creative Cloud apps across desktop, mobile, and web on up to two devices (or virtual machines) at a time, but you may not use the same app on both devices simultaneously.</div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-7" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-7" daa-ll="open-7--What s the best AI photo editor for small businesses">
            What's the best AI photo editor for small businesses?
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-7" id="accordion-1-content-7" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>
              <p>Part of Creative Cloud for teams, Photoshop is the industry standard for precision, AI-powered image editing, making it one of the best AI photo editors to help small businesses create images faster. With Photoshop, teams can:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Upscale images with Topaz Labs .</li>
                <li>Make seamless composites with Harmonize.</li>
                <li>Remove image backgrounds and add or modify content with Generative Fill using leading AI models from Adobe, Google, OpenAI, and more.</li>
              </ul>
            </div></div><div role="heading" aria-level="3" class="descr-term"><button type="button" id="accordion-1-trigger-8" class="accordion-trigger tracking-header" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="accordion-1-content-8" daa-ll="open-8--What s the best AI video generator for small businesses">
            What's the best AI video generator for small businesses?
          <span class="accordion-icon"></span></button></div><div aria-labelledby="accordion-1-trigger-8" id="accordion-1-content-8" hidden="true" class="descr-details"><div>With Creative Cloud for teams, small businesses have access to Firefly — a great option for text-to-video generation. The Firefly AI Video Generator lets teams instantly create high-quality video clips for social media or digital marketing, saving time and money. Learn more.</div></div></div></div>
